    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches, scuffs, and minor dents consistent with regular use. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery, trim panels, and high-contact surfaces. Mechanically the car runs and drives, though it has not been recently serviced and may require attention. Suitable for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a reasonable price.",
